&lt;p&gt;2-&nbsp;Titana&#039;s&nbsp;Super Villian Properties:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1) Titana&#039;s&nbsp;hair is made up of titanium. Titanium is a metal high in strength, her hair has the ability to hit, cut and fight people i.e. choke them.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2) With the snap of her fingers, Titana&nbsp;can create a fire with her titanium hands. By snapping them, it causes titanium dust which is easily flammable. To put out the flames she must put on fire-resistant gloves which contain sodium chloride powder. This sodium chloride powder (salt) does not let the&nbsp;fire come into contact with any air.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3) On Titana&#039;s&nbsp;anatomy, there are metal titanium plates, using her flammable hands, the plates can stretch and protect her due to titanium being ductile. For her titanium to stretch she needs above room temperature heat.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;4) Due to titaniums flammability, Titana&nbsp;has a very volatile personality which tends to make people not want to be around her. Also because her hair is long, strong and sharp, she ends up cutting/hurting people around her accidentally.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Appearance&lt;/strong&gt; property: Iodite&rsquo;s costume is made from 100% solid iodine; consequently, it has a gray, shiny, glowing color. Also, Iodite has purple hair; when she uses her super power, she can blend in and not be recognised by others around her.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Behavior&lt;/strong&gt; property: Due to the strong and unpleasant smell of solid iodine from the costume she wears, that has impregnated in her skin, Iodite tends to stay away from others when at work and to spend most of her time alone.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Super power&lt;/strong&gt; property: Iodite has enhanced regenerative capabilities due to the large amount of iodine in her body; iodine works as a sterilizer for her to recover from outer wounds on her body. Also, her most lethal super power is her ability to create a purple toxic gas; when solid iodine is heated, it turns into a purple gas that is very harmful.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;By looking at the following picture, we recognize some of Iodite&#039;s properties:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Her purple hair&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Her 100% solid iodine costume, that is gray and shinny (the stars on suit represent glow)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The purple gas around her that is iodine&nbsp;gas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is Brominella.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APPEARANCE:&lt;/strong&gt; Brominella&rsquo;s &nbsp;hair, lips and eyes are her defining &nbsp;physical features. Her hair and lips are the same redish brown color as the liquid state of bromine. She wears a two-way mask to cover her eyes, she can see through but others can&rsquo;t see her. She hides her eyes because they are a distinctive amber color, the same color as the gas state of Bromine. Also, in ancient times, prior to the discovery of bromine, royalty would wear fabrics died with Tyrian purple , which is a bromine compound containing a natural dye. Hence why her costume is purple, an acknowledgment to the elements history.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BEHAVIOR:&lt;/strong&gt; She is somewhat of a recluse she stays to herself and rarely , if ever, goes out to social gatherings. She keeps away from situations that may cause other people to come into direct contact with her skin, because if touched it will burn them. This trait comes from the toxic nature of gas and liquid bromine. If exposed to skin, bromine can cause irritation and burns. This quality of hers also forces her to always wear gloves, long sleeves and pants during her regular life. This is also why her costume covers a large part of her neck and why her arms and legs are covered in a protective mesh.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SUPER POWER ABILITY:&lt;/strong&gt; Brominella&rsquo;s main super power is her ability to either shift completely or partially into the gas state of bromine or even excrete it from her pours when necessary in smaller quantities. Bromine can evaporate very easily. Her ability allows her to irritate her victims&#039; skin and eyes, potentially blinding them momentarily, and even attack their respiratory system. In the picture, Brominella is partially transformed. That is why, in the drawing, her lower half is covered in an amber gas.Her secondary ability is that she is able to resistant and slow down flames. When certain materials are soaked in a bromine compound, it makes them flame retardant, hence Brominella&rsquo;s ability.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

