&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Character name: Fluorider&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Appearance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fluorider has yellow skin and green hair because fluorine is pale yellow-green gas.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Behaviour &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;He&rsquo;s extremely agitated and excited due to Fluorine&rsquo;s high reactivity. Fluorine is the most electronegative element, this means, in molecules fluorine attracts electrons more powerfully than any other element can. It&rsquo;s the most reactive of all the elements. Unfortunately not many people like speaking to Fluorider because of his pungent odor, fluorine has a very strong distasteful smell.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Super powers&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fluorider is able to exhale a smelly and highly corrosive gas, because Fluorine is a corrosive gas with a pungent smell.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fluorider wears gloves made of sodium, because when Fluorider releases his fluorine it reacts with the sodium violently and combusts, it creates a small explosion.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is Carbono.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APPEARANCE:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Carbono&rsquo;s suit and armor are made of carbon fiber, because it is highly resistant and light, with a dark‑gray matte color. Also, Carbono has black hair with a dreadlock hairstyle. The African-American man wears a carbon mask only showing his nose and mouth.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BEHAVIOR:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Carbono has no problem being with others because he does not smell, he is not corrosive and has a solid form at room temperature, hence making him a human-friendly superhero. Therefore, he is a very sociable being and we could say that he has a big ego.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SUPER POWER:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Carbono&rsquo;s main ability is to control carbon by changing the covalent bonds between the atoms. In other words, he can transform his body parts into soft materials by being in the graphite state or harden it by being in the diamond state. For obvious reasons, he will use the hardness property of the diamond to deal with enemies. For example, he can change the shape of his diamond fist into a sharp object. Due to his high heat resistant, he has no problem handling with fire-related situations.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is Franny- Please excuse the fact that i have no ability to draw. This took me much longer than i care to admit.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Appearance&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Franny has orange/red hair which is what francium is believed to look like. Similarly she has red eyes due to this being where she stores the majority of her active Francium. She will wear a dark costume that has the ability to turn invisible and is un-affected by the flames cause by francium. Her suit will have a radioactive symbol with 87 in the middle. She will also carry a gun that contains water to be used to increase the severity of explosions.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Behavior&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Franny gets angry very easily and often has to be calmed down before using her powers at inappropriate times. She is also very shy and lonely due to her habit of hiding and keeping to herself. She is not well known but those who know her, love her and are constantly trying to see more of her.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Super Power&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;She has two abilities. Her first being her ability to become invisible. This is because Francium has such a short half-life, she is often gone before you realize she is there. She also has the ability to shoot francium out of her eyes which is reactive with almost every substance. Especially water. If her shot comes into any contact with water- often shot from her gun the explosion will become massive.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;The Zincanator&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Appearance:&lt;/strong&gt; Zinc is described as a&nbsp;silvery-white metal with a blue tinge, that is where the inspiration for the colors used come from as they are present throughout his appearance. Although not very visible in the image there are 30 decorative dots placed through his appearance to symbolize Zinc&#039;s atomic number. He has a large tower shield as his weapon of choice as Zinc is most commonly used to galvanize other metals to protect them from corrosion. The crest on his shield is actually my attempt to draw the German coat of arms, to pay tribute to the German chemist, Andreas Marggraf, who discovered the element of Zinc. The presences of blue-green flame/flare on the shield and eyes represents when Zinc burns it produce a bright blue-green flame/flare.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Behavior:&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;The Zincanator is a calm, cool and collected and thinks clearly through all his options&nbsp;in all situations due to Zinc&#039;s extremely high melting point. Also, he does not go out often and covers his skin fully as Zinc oxides very quickly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Superpowers:&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp; Zinc plays a large role in a large number of enzymes in the human body. The things it affects are immune system, the senses and has an effect on the healing of wounds. I propose that The Zincanator&#039;s power to have a healing factor and the ability to boost his body&#039;s capabilities to due the role of enzymes in the body, making him a sort of superhuman.&lt;/p&gt;

