&lt;p&gt;When combined with nitrate to create silver nitrate (AgNO3), you have a white odourless solid that is often used in medicine. The compound has disinfectant and antimicrobial properties which your character could use to their advantage. If you character gets hurt by their enemy, they can easily get access to silver nitrate and use it as a form of pain relief so that they can quickly heal themselves.&lt;/p&gt;

